@startuml 态势感知与预案生成时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "EventCollector" as EColl
participant "EventNormalizer" as EN
participant "CorrelationEngine" as CE
participant "RiskEvaluator" as RE
participant "PlanGenerator" as PGen

EColl -> EColl : 采集多源原始事件
EColl -> EN : normalize(raw_event)
EN -> EN : 统一时间戳、分配任务编号、分类事件
EN --> EColl : 返回标准化Event
EColl -> CE : 提交标准化事件流
CE -> CE : 串联攻击链与响应链
CE -> RE : evaluate_risk(chains)
RE -> RE : 计算影响范围与严重程度
RE --> CE : 返回风险等级
CE -> Frontend : WebSocket推送态势更新
Frontend --> User : 展示态势总览面板

User -> Frontend : 点击生成预案
Frontend -> PGen : generate_plan(risk_assessment)
PGen -> PGen : 匹配模板并结合案例生成处置步骤
PGen --> Frontend : 返回预案详情
Frontend --> User : 展示预案及处置步骤

@enduml
